{"tid":1595186,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解黑警拉完人要急急提堂?　可能係借法庭令被捕人封口","createTime":"2019-09-26T02:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T02:35:15.000Z","uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7fee819001dabe2f49b2d516b9d122d1e92278b","tid":1595186,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"抗爭已經超過100日<br />\n被捕義士、無辜嘅市民超過1500人<br />\n近排黑警每逢拉到人都急急腳提堂<br />\n可能同法庭審訊程序有關<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講<br />\n每一個CASE係第一次提堂前<br />\n傳媒都可以繼續報道相關嘅案件<br />\n但只要第一次提堂<br />\n即使只係過一過堂<br />\n傳媒就唔可以再報道「法庭上披露案情」以外嘅野<br />\n亦因為咁記者係唔可能再被捕人做訪問<br />\n因為被告一評論案情都會做成妨礙司法公正<br />\n所以近排好多義士被捕後<br />\n幾乎第二日就會提堂<br />\n就算保釋到出黎<br />\n一單案閒閒地都要玩幾個月<br />\n對黑警黎講告唔告得入唔係重點<br />\n只係想搞鳩你<br />\n玩完冇後果，點解唔玩？"},{"pid":"510c194fbcfa131fc03da6ef8162193750e1a67b","tid":1595186,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"仲有鳩拉入唔到係完全無後果無成本更加無懲罰<br />\n無成本可以玩野點解唔拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55718a2c6df064cbb9f9ea03755d5a56b78010f5","tid":1595186,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"［香港獨立！唯一辦法！］<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWKL3KV.jpg&h=63206eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGKzOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGKzOZ.jpg&h=bcba39e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqWCakp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqWCakp.jpg&h=6804524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFLjcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFLjcd.